# Hello World - Your First CURSED Program
# 
# This is the traditional first program in any language.
# In CURSED, we use 'vibez' for I/O operations and 'spill' to print.

# Import the vibez module for output operations
yeet "vibez"

# Print a welcoming message
vibez.spill("🔥 Hello, CURSED World! 🔥")

# You can print multiple values in one call
vibez.spill("Welcome to", "CURSED", "programming!")

# Print with different data types
vibez.spill("The answer is:", 42)
vibez.spill("CURSED is awesome:", based)  # 'based' means true

